name: Uppercut Deluxe Essentials Washkit
description: Formulated naturally, this essentials kit comes with Shampoo, Conditioner, our famous goats milk soap and a black pocket comb. A great gift or just to buff yourself out.

name: Uppercut Deluxe Soap
description: Uppercut Deluxe Soap is specially formulate to be Unfragranced and made with Goat's milk and Oatmeal to gently exfoliate and cleanse your skin. It all natural and contains tested and approved ingredients.

name: Stance Women's Bondage Tights
description:
We’re giving you the ultimate leg up with our all-time sexiest style. The Bondage tights live up to their name, with a skintight nylon build and sheer paneling. Naughty by nature.


FIT: Waist-high
S/M: 5' - 5'6" (85-145lbs)
L/XL: 5'7' - 5'10" (110-145lbs)

NOTE: These seem to run a little on the small side so order a size up if you are unsure!

We Cannot Accept Returns On These! Unless They Are Faulty! Thanks!

name: Stance Women's Dotted Lines
description: Sign on the Dotted Lines and repeat after us: “don’t match, don’t matter.” Treat your feet to the highly-individualized attention they deserve with grape-toed stripes on one side, purple-heeled polka-dots on the other—we made both with the same amount of combed cotton love. After all, two lefts don’t make a right.

name: Stance Women's Santiago
description: Is it Chile in here? It must be, because the Santiago sock feels like getting a stamp in our passports every time we slip on that buttery soft combed cotton. Call it a little piece of the world you can store in your closet.

name: Stance Women's Get In Line
description: What’s the use of running in circles when you could Get-N-Line with our multi-hued striped socks? Catch your breath with icy-cool mint and charcoal color bands that wrap your feet up in cozy combed cotton, while our springy arch support shows them some love.

name: Stance Women's Hombre
description: We do details with military precision, so our Hombre socks are the perfect blend of surplus-store greens and khakis without all the bells and whistles. Just plush combed cotton, perfect color blocking, and a touch of elastic to keep them standing at attention.

name: Stance Women's Glimmer
description:
Two socks are fine but three are divine—triple up with this three-pack of our favorite everyday styles. They’re all made with our buttery-soft cotton and a little extra support for arches and heels. All for one and three for all.

These really have to be seen in person as photos do not do them justice! they shimmer and glimmer in the light! Perfect for girls who love a bit of BLING!

name: Stance Women's Galactacat
description: When we tapped Aussie stylist Imogene Barron as one of our Punks & Poets, we had hoped for her first sock design would be a little "out there," a short order for the fashion icon who's made bold originality something of a trademark. She delivered tenfold with her Galactacat socks, a cosmic-crazed print featuring some space-floating-felines. Tie-dye cool from a distance, out of this world up close-theres even a meow message on the soles. We'd be purring if we knew how.

name: Stance Socks - Sutton
description: There’s a certain elegance in simplicity. For proof, slip on the Sutton. The sock’s chunky knit merino wool provides a premium feel and wicks moisture from your feet. For additional comfort, the Sutton also features a deep heel pocket and Y Gore Seam. And to complement its classic appearance, the sock sports a leather badge. For everything you need—and nothing you don’t—slip on the Sutton.

name: Stance Socks Sawtooth
description: Stance’s Sawtooth looks as good as it performs. Thanks to its premium merino wool, the sock wicks moisture from your feet while cradling them in comfort. A deep heel pocket and medium cushioning provide additional comfort and durability. And for extra style, these socks sport a chunky knit and leather badge. The Sawtooth is perfect for kicking back—or stepping outside and exploring the unknown.

name: Stance Wittlake Snow Socks
description: The Wittlake stems from good ideas and good people. For this sock Stance partnered with Scotty Wittlake and Injinji. The Wittlake features Injinji’s patented five-toe design, which properly aligns toes for natural movement. To enhance circulation and reduce fatigue, the sock provides varying degrees of compression throughout the lower leg. And to keep things extra comfy, the Wittlake sports a beefy shin cushion, arch support, and a deep heel pocket. Follow your toes to freedom.

name: Stance Snow Socks Baldface Lodge
description: Those in the know speak of Baldface with a blend of reverence and awe. Nestled within the backcountry of British Columbia, the lodge benefits from an abundance of snow and epic terrain. Needless to say, it provides the perfect laboratory for developing this premium sock. The sock’s Thermolite fibers offer plenty of warmth while its seamless toe closure and Y Gore Seam keep things comfy. The Baldface also features left and right-specific cushioning to maximize comfort and performance. The sock’s traction control ensures it stays in place—even when you’re throwing down that double cork. Stance’s Baldface provides everything you need for enduring winter days—well, everything but courage.

name: Stance Snow Socks Boot Monkey
description:
On your feet or as a sock monkey, these babies are made to be loved.

Merino Wool to get your feet in check whether your on piste, lapping the park, hiking the backcountry or heading out on a late night urban mission!

name: Stance Redemption Snow Sock Mens
description: One love. Two socks. Stance’s Redemption provides comfort for your feet and positive vibes for your soul. The sock’s deep heel pocket and elastic arch and ankle support cradle your feet and provide a plush ride. To ensure the sock moves with you throughout your journeys, the Redemption also sports an instep flex panel. And to eliminate friction, the sock features a seamless toe closure. Slip on the Redemption and kick back in luxury.

name: Stance Leblanc 13 Snow Socks Men's
description: At Stance, we’re always stoked to collaborate with Mikey LeBlanc. Like Mikey, the LeBlanc 13 is a reliable workhorse. Made from merino wool, this medium cushion sock offers plenty of warmth in a streamlined package. The sock’s Y Gore Seam and instep flex panel cradle your feet and provide a plush ride. The LeBlanc 13’s elastic arch and ankle support also ensure it stays in place. As an added bonus, the sock’s camouflage aids in evading the police. After all, you never know how those midnight rail sessions might end!!!!

name: Stance Elephont Mens Snow Socks
description: Don Pendleton’s art is iconic. Whether on skateboards or canvases, it demands attention. Part of Stance’s Artist Series, the Elephont is the most comfortable art you’ll ever own. The sock’s Y Gore Seam and elastic arch and ankle support provide a plush feel while its instep flex panel hugs your feet. Treat your eyes and your feet to the Elephont.

name: Stance Holden Snow Socks Mens
description: Subtle—perhaps no better word captures the ethos of Holden. For this collaboration with the brand, we focused on understatement. Stance’s Holden blends classic styling with carefully considered features. The sock’s merino wool provides light cushioning, comfort, and warmth. Thanks to a Y Gore Seam and an elastic arch and ankle support, it also cradles your feet and stays in place. Stance’s Holden offers everything you need—and nothing you don’t.

name: Stance Clarissa Women's Snow Socks
description: Stance teamed up with Holden to create the Clarissa. At home lapping the mountain or embracing après sessions, this sock offers plenty of comfort. Its merino wool keeps you warm and provides a plush feel. To cradle your feet, it sports a Y Gore Seam and an elastic arch and ankle support. Slip on the Clarissa and step outside.

name: Stance Supernova Womens Snow Socks
description: Stance’s Supernova is the perfect companion for embracing winter. Its merino wool provides warmth and a plush feel. To cradle your feet in comfort, the sock also sports a Y Gore Seam and an elastic arch and ankle support. And to ensure the Supernova moves with your feet, it also features an instep flex panel. Don’t be fooled by its good looks, this sock thrives on the rigors of winter.

"But thats what you get when Wu-Tang raised you" - Macklemore

The Wu Tang sock from Stance. Part of our exclusive Reserve collection, the Wu Tang stands as a tribute to the greatest Hip Hop group ever, incarnated on our silky smooth socks. Walk the walk and let your socks be your mouthpiece.

name: Penny Skateboards Christian Hosoi Signature Nickel
description:
Christian Hosoi, known for his raw dynamic style and approach to skateboarding brings his legendary rising sun graphic to the 27" Nickel skateboard. Featuring an epic graphic wrap and custom transparent griptape, the Hosoi Signature model is a must have for your Penny collection.

This Penny Nickel 27” is matched with Custom 4” Hosoi powder-coated Penny trucks, Black 59mm 78A super smooth Penny wheels, colour coded high tensile bolts and Penny Abec7 bearings.

name: Penny Holiday Resin 27"
description:
Waves flat? This resin-style board will have you feeling like you`re trimming down the line of a 4-6ft wall at your local break. Sidewalk surfing styles!

This graphic wrapped Penny Nickel 27” is matched with 4” powder-coated Penny trucks, Clear blue 59mm 78A super smooth Penny wheels, colour coded high tensile bolts and Penny Abec7 bearings.

name: Penny Classic Nickel 27" Hoverboard
description:
The Penny Nickel 27” Skateboard is the big brother of the Penny Original 22”.

THIS BOARD SERIOUSLY LIGHTS UP IN THE DARK!

For those who appreciate a little extra plastic under your feet, this ticks all the boxes. Featuring our secret plastic formula, this Penny Nickel 27” is matched with Custom 4” raw Penny trucks, Black 59mm 78A super smooth Penny wheels, and Penny Abec7 bearings. Please note, Nickel owners have reported drastic increases in summery vibrations.

Danny skates this board and reports that the glow in the dark feature is amazing!!!

name: Penny Classic Hoverboard 22"
description:
The Penny Original 22” Skateboard embodies what Penny is all about – fun, freedom & the highest quality components possible.

Featuring our secret plastic formula, this Penny Original 22” Glow in the dark deck is matched with Custom 3” Black Penny trucks, Black 59mm 78A super smooth Penny wheels, and Penny Abec7 bearings. Please note, purchasing this skateboard may result in overwhelming radness.

name: Penny Pastels Lemon 22"
description:
One for the ladies, or men who like pastel colours, who are we to judge?

Refresh this season with the sugary shades and candy coloured hues of mint, lilac and citrus lemon.

This Penny 22” is matched with 3” powder-coated Penny trucks, 59mm 78A super smooth Penny wheels, GOLD accent high tensile bolts and Penny Abec7 bearings.

name: Penny Pastel Lilac 22"
description:
One for the ladies, or men who like pastel colors, who are we to judge?

Refresh this season with the sugary shades and candy coloured hues of mint, lilac and citrus lemon.

This Penny 22” is matched with 3” powder-coated Penny trucks, 59mm 78A super smooth Penny wheels, GOLD accent high tensile bolts and Penny Abec7 bearings.

name: Penny Holiday Polka 22"
description:
From the 'good old days' of fast cars, grease lightning and milk bars, we bring you the Polka board! The simplistically stylish design of the graphic wrapped board will have you standing out in vintage style.

This graphic wrapped Penny Original 22” is matched with 3” powder-coated Penny trucks, bright red 59mm 78A super smooth Penny wheels, colour coded high tensile bolts and Penny Abec7 bearings.

name: Penny Organic Turquoise 22"
description:
Penny Organic Skateboards feature a biodegradable deck that eventually breaks down when completely immersed in soil. Until then, Penny Organic Skateboards last just as long and ride just as well as a standard Penny. Every Organic Skateboard comes wrapped in a printed hessian tote bag to ensure you're skating in fine style.

Penny Organic completes are sized 22 inches x 6 inches and manufactured from high quality, 100% bio-degradable plastic, with Penny custom 3 inch trucks, 59mm 78A super smooth Penny wheels and Abec 7 bearings.

name: Penny Holiday Resin 22"
description:
Waves flat? This resin-style board will have you feeling like you`re trimming down the line of a 4-6ft wall at your local break. Sidewalk surfing styles!


This graphic wrapped Penny Original 22” is matched with 3” powder-coated Penny trucks, Clear blue 59mm 78A super smooth Penny wheels, colour coded high tensile bolts and Penny Abec7 bearings.

name: Uppercut Deluxe Matt Clay
description:
Uppercut Deluxe Matt Clay makes it easy to achieve a no-fuss messy look. Don’t let the thick consistency fool you, the clay does what you tell it to, effortlessly piecing out hair to give a pliable, re-workable style.

Directions for use: Spread a small amount in dry palms and fingers and work through dry hair, styling as desired.

name: Uppercut Deluxe Featherweight
description: Don’t be fooled by the name, just because this wax is light doesn’t mean it can’t pack a punch. Featherweight has plenty of tack and dry finish for a natural looking hold. Great for messy quiffs and textured styles. Another great feature with this product is that it’s water soluble which means you get a great dry look without any build up or residue. Without a doubt the great all rounder.

name: Uppercut Deluxe Monster Hold
description: For those who like it real strong we present to you our Monster Hold pomade. Extra powerful, sweat resistant and great for all styles.

name: Uppercut Deluxe Deluxe Pomade
description:
Uppercut Deluxe Pomade is a water-soluble product suitable for a diverse range of styles but particularly popular with fellas rocking a slickback, quiff or mohawk. Its unique formula means it will wash out easily leaving no residue. The Pomade gives control and definition without the weight of traditional pomades.

Directions for use: Rub a small amount into palms and work through dry hair to style as desired.

Size: 100ml.

name: Uppercut Deluxe Shave Cream
description:
Willy O’Shea drove into old Sydney town after years on the road with the Jimmy Sharman boxing troupe. The Great Depression had lifted and it was time to settle. First job on the list was a shave and a haircut before he started looking for a job and a pretty lady. He strolled out of the Barbershop feeling like a million bucks.

With that feeling in mind we are pleased to introduce to you our deluxe lemongrass Shave Cream. Made for the common man who wants to step it up a notch. Contains Menthol for cooling and Coconut oil to aid in blemish control for a clean finish. Can also be used with a shaving brush for ultimate lather.

name: Uppercut Deluxe Aftershave Moisturiser
description:
For you fellas rocking a short crop, this all-rounder is for you. Perfect as a daily moisturiser, the lotion nourishes the skin, minimises oiliness and reduces the appearance of large pores. Leaves a no sheen, no fuss, matt finish. It’s non-greasy, non-sticky and will absorb immediately.

Directions for use: Apply generously to clean, dry skin on your head and face. Rub in thoroughly to achieve matt finish. Use morning and evening for optimal results.

name: Uppercut Deluxe Shampoo
description:
While your lady might argue otherwise, one product is all you need to do the job. The all-in-one shampoo and body wash is laced with peppermint extract for an energising boost and is gentle enough to use daily (yes, you should be showering that frequently).

Directions for use: Apply to wet hair and body, create a rich lather and rinse. Repeat if desired. Suitable for daily use.

name: Uppercut Deluxe Conditioner
description:
Follow up a shampoo with this conditioning treatment that will restore your hair to its former glory, restoring body to make it more manageable.

Directions for use: For best results, use after Uppercut Shampoo / Bodywash. Remove excess water from hair, massage into hair and scalp. Rinse thoroughly.

name: Uppercut Deluxe Quiff Roller
description: ife getting you down? Need to get more lift in your quiff? Feeling like your hair is a little limp? Need more air in your hair? Well, get ready for lift-off with the new Uppercut Deluxe Quiff Roller. We will also have an instructional video up on the site soon to show you how we roll. Stay tuned…

name: Uppercut Deluxe Pocket Comb
description: Tough plastic comb with wide teeth to get nice clean comb lines through your quiff or slickback. Keep it sharp and slick with this handy pocket comb.
